        <div class="w3-content w3-container w3-padding-64" id=
        "poetry">
          <h3 class="w3-center">
            KAREN DOESN'T BELIEVE IN OBJECTIVE SCIENCE
          </h3>
          <p class="w3-center"></p>
          <p>
            <em>NARRATION:</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>There is</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>no light here – palmed the evening and a month’s
            prescription, set them cooling</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>over the eyelid, so that it was heavy the room
            undone by overhead</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>fan and the distant siren this the afterlife of
            mermaid song</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>that unmoored ships</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>drifting</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>water risen to the upper lip</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>lulled</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>to</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>sleep</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>in the dark</em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
